This paper deals with a sequential decision-making problem using deep neural networks and efficient exploration mechanisms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves classification, sentiment analysis, and regression, which are common topics in sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). Additionally, the use of deep neural networks suggests that cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) could also be a relevant sub-category.
